episodes.title: #29 Peter Young & Cults
episodes.description: Author Peter Young joins the podcast to talk about his memoir Stop The Tall Man, Save The Tiger which chronicles his time in a religious cult. The docs continue the discussion about cults before finishing up on the Mental Health Tip of the Day.  00:00 - Top 5 slang terms & dog discrimination 10:10 - Peter Young 52:18 - Cults 1:15:34 - #MHToD
